Sea fishing (Net)
Main Skill: Fishing
Max Efficiency: 160%

Along the shoreline, you find a secluded spot and cast your net into the calm waters, enjoying the peaceful solitude of sea fishing.

The Sea fishing (Net) activity is a Fishing activity.

Locations

This activity can be done at the following locations:

  • Beach of Woes in Jarvonia
  • Granfiddich Shores in Grand Duchy of Trellin-Erdwise

Requirements

Skill Level Requirements:

  • At least Fishing lvl. 1.

Keyword Requirements:

  • Have Fishing net equipped.

Visibility

This activity is always visible.
